5:
The place that Suizen was talking
about is just up ahead! We need to
hurry before they start the ritual!
8:
The closer we get, the more those
guys keep popping up. It must
mean we're in the right spot.
12:
...This is the same place I fought
those spies trying to resurrect
Orochi.
17: Does that mean they're at it again?!
21:
It's just like what Suizen said. These
guys just don't know when to give
up, do they?
25:
...We have to hurry, it'll be starting
soon.
38:
The only thing you should have
been expecting is a taste of my
blade!
40:
Don't get so ahead of yourself... You
fool!
44:
Well look at that! He's a stubborn
one, but he gets the job done.
53:
Dammit! Destroying it is the only
way to put an end to this once and
for all!
63:
What's this? ...Aramasa and
Karasahi just vibrated... Could it be?
67:
...Are you the one who smiled... at
me?
74:
All this time, I've been dreaming
about this moment. To finally meet
you once more.
76:
...But why? Why have I been so
obsessed with this idea...
79: What do you want from me?
84:
If you cannot forgive me for my
actions, do as you—
88:
It is a spirit that feeds off of hate...
You are far from the only one who
has been ensnarled by its trap...
90:
Like you before them, my previous
partners have also fallen prey to it.
And for that, this makes it personal!
93:
You've gotta be yanking my tail!
You're telling me that this serpent is
what you've been looking for this
whole time?
98:
Don't listen to what that thing says,
Yakumo! It's trying to trick you!
102:
Yakumo... Is punishment what you've
been seeking this whole time?
105:
We're here to help you, just get back,
please!
110:
It was only supposed to be me and
her.
112:
I wanted to know... Why she smiled
at me. To ask for her forgiveness...
114: That's what I've been looking for.
118:
...Then there's nothing wrong with
that! So let's cross out dying from
today's agenda!
128:
Aramasa... Karasahi... I'm sorry I've
ignored your warnings. Please, lend
me your strength once more!
139: I will not be your meal, serpent.
142:
Until the day comes when I can
meet her again, my search
continues.
151:
I can't believe you were almost
tricked into becoming some yokai's
meal... You're more naive that I
thought.
153:
But you did return in one piece, so I'll
ignore those details.
157: I am in your debt... I mean...
165:
A bit dramatic, are we? I helped you
and now it's your turn to help me. I
could always use someone like you
on my side.
170:
I would prefer to be stationed with
Alk... If everyone is fine with it.
174:
I have no objections. This
arrangement should prove fruitful
for us all.
178:
And in the meantime, I will continue
to chase after the one I seek.
183: ...You don't give up easily, do you?
188:
I can't stop until I find her. Can I ask
for your help once more?
196: Then I am in your debt... Again.
206:
Looks like we'll have to do a
welcome party then! I'll be sure to
prepare something extra special for
the occasion!
213:
Someday. Somewhere. We will meet
again.
